    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/c7fdbc6b96848cfdc30879ef47dd3646.webp?t=1762592363\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Action Roguelike  +  Turn-based Card Deckbuilder</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/525550aa84b88b2288ea2f547f20a290.poster.avif?t=1762592363\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/525550aa84b88b2288ea2f547f20a290.webm?t=1762592363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rogue Drone Hunter</strong> is a unique action roguelike blending real-time combat with strategic card play.  Shoot and dodge your way through relentless waves of rogue AI machines while carefully constructing your ultimate battle deck to unleash powerful card combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/f855a0167b057296a782b7ced7701784.poster.avif?t=1762592363\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/f855a0167b057296a782b7ced7701784.webm?t=1762592363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set on the outskirts of the futuristic city of <strong>Elysia</strong>, you are a Hunter tasked with eliminating deadly rogue drones and uncovering the truth behind a mysterious machine invasion. Explore, collect powerful cards, and unlock game-changing perks to defend humanity. Team up with your drone companion to unravel the rogue machine threat.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Diverse Deckbuilding</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your ultimate deck from hundreds of unique cards and create powerful synergies to obliterate your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/bf53916feb37ba39d85838ab6a78bcb1.poster.avif?t=1762592363\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/bf53916feb37ba39d85838ab6a78bcb1.webm?t=1762592363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Real-Time Action Shooter</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in intense shooting bullet-hell combat, while dodging attacks and taking down relentless boss machines and enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Roguelike Replayability</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover new surprises as you venture beyond Elysia.  Face a variety of cards, perks, and enemies that challenge your skills and ensure every run feels unique.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Befriend Unique Characters</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage with diverse personalities through compelling conversations, and uncover the secrets of Elysia and the mysterious fog that surrounds the city.  Will you be able to rally humanity to stand against the escalating machine threat?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/fced4cc9cca9b14d77515381166fc775.poster.avif?t=1762592363\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/fced4cc9cca9b14d77515381166fc775.webm?t=1762592363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Tactical Terrain</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience fully destructible terrain and objects.  Take cover in bushes or demolish structures to gain the advantage. Surprise your foes by setting off explosive traps and turning the battlefield to your favor.</p>",
